My sweetest little potato, thank you for spending so many wonderful years with me and being the best companion I could have ever asked for. 
You filled my life with joy, love, and memories I’ll always treasure. 
You will forever be in my heart, and I miss you so much already. I love you Puga-chan.❤️ 🐶

For the past few months I have been working with @courbetofficial , the first ecological jeweler from Place Vendome in Paris, to co-create 5 jewellery designs made with 18K recycled gold and lab-grown diamonds. 
Inspired by their cosmic theme-jewellery, I decided to create a special charm shaped after part of my own signature, and included both white and colourful diamonds. 💫
I couldn’t be happier with the outcome! 🥰
This collection will be available for a year, starting today… and would make for a great Valentine’s Day gift. 💝 You can find the link in my story!
#CourbetMuse #sustainablejewelry #ad

To celebrate the launch of my collaboration with @courbetofficial we are doing a giveaway! 🎊 🌟
3 winners will be selected in 10 days from today, and will get a coupon of 2 000€ to spend on my collection. 

All the pieces are made from recycled 18K gold, and lab grown diamonds. ✨

Rules to enter:
- Follow @CourbetOfficial & @itsmarziapie
- Like the post
- Tag 2 friends in the comments 

Don’t hesitate to save the post and share in story. 

Good luck! 🌸

#CourbetMuse #sustainablejewelry #ad

It’s no secret that I ✨ love ✨ knitting, so I am honoured @weareknitters asked me to design some knits 🧶 which are now available on their website as kits! I drew inspiration from early spring flowers, like cherry blossom and boke 🌸 and wanted to make some good transition pieces for the season. I hope you like the styles, and if you pick up a kit, I hope you will have a great time knitting!! 😉 🎉 #ad
